个人简介
			
			&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;宁波镇海人，文学博士。现为浙江大学国际文化学系副教授，硕士生导师，美国芝加哥大学访问学者，浙江省美学学会副秘书长。现出版专著《追寻真诚：卢梭与审美现代性》等。主要研究领域：伦理与政治美学、文化批评及启蒙思想史。
&nbsp;&nbsp;

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;FanYunisanAssociateProfessorattheCollegeofMediaandInternationalCulture(CMIC),ZhejiangUniversity（ZJU）.HereceivedhisBAandPhDfromZhejiangUniversity.HewasavisitingscholaratthedepartmentofphilosophyintheUniversityofChicagofromSeptembertoDecemberin2011.HeisappointedasthedeputysecretaryofZhejiangAestheticsAssociation.&nbsp;&nbsp;Atpresent,hespecializesinethicsandaesthetics,literarytheory,culturalcriticism,withaparticularfocusonwesternEnlightenmentthoughtin18thcentury.HiscurrentbookPursueSincerity:RousseauandaestheticmodernitywaspublishedbyShanghaiRenminpressin2013.
&nbsp;
			
				
